# VEHICLE::CAN_ANCHOR_BOAT_HERE_IGNORE_PLAYERS

## Summary
This is the same as the above function but will ignore any players who are stood on the vehicle

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle

## Returns
* **BOOL**
